description: Contains 1 PDB structure and no sequences
3 PDBs say that is a biotin carboxylase B-domain, SwissProt indicates tRNA synthase
6 PDBs agree that this is a gef-domain, while sequences propose either uncharachterised or other things

Poor domain structure. Seems like there has been incorrect chopping of this protein since one of the alpha helices comprising this domain has not been included completely and it appears as to be part of two different domains.
